 Spin Chains with Finite Range Interaction</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Communications in Mathematical Physics</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/9ac58e8bd31de3ff0ea02d5317f8a5f1"><gtr:id>9ac58e8bd31de3ff0ea02d5317f8a5f1</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Its A</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2008-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/95DA3472-93EE-448B-87A3-778F8AD58DF4"><gtr:id>95DA3472-93EE-448B-87A3-778F8AD58DF4</gtr:id><gtr:title>On an Average over the Gaussian Unitary Ensemble</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>International Mathematics Research Notices</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/1d337391c6480c8ebdc9d2c456848f0f"><gtr:id>1d337391c6480c8ebdc9d2c456848f0f</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Mezzadri F</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2009-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/0ED3BDE4-82F4-48B8-A6B1-DC4C4407C2CB"><gtr:id>0ED3BDE4-82F4-48B8-A6B1-DC4C4407C2CB</gtr:id><gtr:title>Double Scaling Limit of Semiclassical Orthogonal Polynomials in the Center of a Tree and the Painleve 1 Equation</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>International Mathematics Research Notices</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/7810a2a551ff1ad5a47ab8a642d5d49e"><gtr:id>7810a2a551ff1ad5a47ab8a642d5d49e</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Mo M</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2009-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/2F69CF55-B53C-4CD6-B26C-DD24D46E6C88"><gtr:id>2F69CF55-B53C-4CD6-B26C-DD24D46E6C88</gtr:id><gtr:title>Universality in the Two Matrix Model with a Monomial Quartic and a General Even Polynomial Potential</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Communications in Mathematical Physics</gtr:parentPublicationTitl